msgid "Use `list` as the primary query entrypoint for this resource."
msgstr "将 `list` 作为此资源的主要查询入口。"

#: src/lifeos_cli/cli_support/resources/area/parser.py:51
msgid "Use areas to group visions and other higher-level planning objects."
msgstr "使用 `area` 对 `vision` 和其他更高层规划对象进行分组。"

#: src/lifeos_cli/cli_support/resources/area/parser.py:52
#: src/lifeos_cli/cli_support/resources/people/parser.py:55
#: src/lifeos_cli/cli_support/resources/tag/parser.py:44
#: src/lifeos_cli/cli_support/resources/task/parser.py:65
#: src/lifeos_cli/cli_support/resources/vision/parser.py:50
msgid "Use the `batch` namespace for multi-record write operations."
msgstr "使用 `batch` 命名空间进行多记录写操作。"

#: src/lifeos_cli/cli_support/resources/area/parser.py:53
#: src/lifeos_cli/cli_support/resources/note/parser.py:63
#: src/lifeos_cli/cli_support/resources/people/parser.py:56
