msgstr "搜索 `note`"

#: src/lifeos_cli/cli_support/resources/note/parser_actions.py:170
msgid "Search notes by keyword tokens."
msgstr "通过关键字标记搜索 `note`。"

#: src/lifeos_cli/cli_support/resources/note/parser_actions.py:173
msgid ""
"The current implementation uses a PostgreSQL-backed ILIKE token search.\n"
"Each token is matched against note content, and any matching token keeps\n"
"the note in the result set."
msgstr ""
"当前的实现使用 PostgreSQL 支持的 ILIKE 令牌搜索。\n"
"每个令牌都与 `note` 内容进行匹配，并且任何匹配的令牌都会保留\n"
"结果集中的 `note`。"

#: src/lifeos_cli/cli_support/resources/note/parser_actions.py:186
msgid "Results use the same summary format as `lifeos note list`."
msgstr "结果使用与 `lifeos note list ` 相同的摘要格式。"

#: src/lifeos_cli/cli_support/resources/note/parser_actions.py:187
msgid "Multi-word queries are split into tokens and matched with OR semantics."
msgstr "多词查询被拆分为标记并使用 OR 语义进行匹配。"

#: src/lifeos_cli/cli_support/resources/note/parser_actions.py:191
