msgstr "执行批量 `note` 操作"

#: src/lifeos_cli/cli_support/resources/note/parser_actions.py:367
msgid "Run operations that target multiple notes in a single command."
msgstr "在单条命令中执行针对多个 `note` 的操作。"

#: src/lifeos_cli/cli_support/resources/note/parser_actions.py:370
msgid ""
"Use this namespace for bulk workflows so the CLI keeps a stable shape as\n"
"new note capabilities are introduced."
msgstr ""
"使用此命名空间进行批量工作流程，以便 CLI 保持稳定的形状\n"
"引入了新的 `note` 功能。"

#: src/lifeos_cli/cli_support/resources/note/parser_actions.py:384
msgid "Batch commands currently accept note IDs directly."
msgstr "批处理命令目前直接接受 `note` ID。"

#: src/lifeos_cli/cli_support/resources/note/parser_actions.py:385
msgid "Future note batch operations should be added under this namespace."
msgstr "以后的 `note` 批量操作应该添加到这个命名空间下。"

#: src/lifeos_cli/cli_support/resources/note/parser_actions.py:392
msgid "operations"
msgstr "操作"

#: src/lifeos_cli/cli_support/resources/note/parser_actions.py:393
msgid "operation"
msgstr "操作"

