msgstr "在一个命令中删除多个 `note`。"

#: src/lifeos_cli/cli_support/resources/note/parser_actions.py:454
msgid "This command mirrors `lifeos note delete`, but works across many note IDs."
msgstr "此命令镜像 `lifeos note delete`，但适用于许多 `note` ID。"

#: src/lifeos_cli/cli_support/resources/note/parser_actions.py:462
