"Use it for the human partner and, when useful, a named automation "
"identity so tasks, events, and timelogs can distinguish who the work "
"belongs to."
msgstr "将其用于人类合作伙伴；必要时也可使用具名自动化身份，以便 `task`、`event` 和 `timelog` 能区分工作归属。"

